The paper deals with physical layer security in relay networks, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of jamming and relays also falls under the category of network security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions interference cancellation, which is a technique used in multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems (cs.MM). Finally, the proposed algorithm involves selecting relay nodes and setting thresholds, which can be considered as a control system (cs.SY).
